###GET rules
GET http://localhost:9090/rules
Accept: application/json


### Delete thing
DELETE http://localhost:9090/rules/192.168.1.103:55443

###create time rule
POST http://localhost:9090/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "testRule",
  "enabled": true,
  "trigger": {
    "time": "0:53",
    "type": "TimeTrigger",
    "onValue": true
  },
  "effect": {
    "property": {
      "type": "boolean",
      "thing": "192.168.1.101:55443",
      "id": "on"
    },
    "type": "SetEffect",
    "value": true
  }
}

###create rule
POST http://localhost:9090/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "testRule",
  "enabled": true,
  "trigger": {
    "property": {
      "type": "boolean",
      "id": "on",
      "thing": "192.168.1.103:55443"
    },
    "type": "BooleanTrigger",
    "onValue": true
  },
  "effect": {
    "property": {
      "type": "boolean",
      "thing": "192.168.1.103:55443",
      "id": "on"
    },
    "type": "SetEffect",
    "value": true
  }
}